properties.Name: CharacteristicType
properties.Description:
A type of characteristic associated with an individual.

Ex:
- Special seating required
- Special dietary requirement
- Hard of hearing
- Visual impairment
- Life-threatening allergy(s)
- Non-life-threatening allergy(s)
- Cardia Health Issues
- Diplomatic Person
- Do Not Fly (US)
- Exit Row Qualified
- Number Of Children
- Favorite Color
